README for NUOPC wrapped Noah LSM
---------------------------------------

Dependencies:
  - ESMF v7.0.0 beta
  
Build:
  - Set environment variable ESMFMKFILE to point to the esmf.mk of your ESMF
    installation.
  - gmake
  - outputs mod/NUOPC_Model_Noah.mod and lib/NUOPC_Model_Noah.o for use in
    NUOPC application.
  - generates makefile fragment for NUOPC_Model_Noah module and object locations

Code structure:
  - Makefile - Makefile that is based on the standard esmf.mk mechanism.
  - src/NUOPC_Model_Noah.F90 - The Noah specialized NUOPC MODEL component
  - /UncoupledNoahTest - Standalone single component driver test
  - README - This file
